{"tid":397650,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"毒遊越南芽莊之旅","createTime":"2017-09-12T15:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T16:55:22.000Z","uid":16176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c18e87d458c03df376ec9c96191fbc244d983888","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完芽莊 想分享下<br />\n有無巴絲都想/去過芽莊<br />\n可以一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前未去過越南 今次係第一次<br />\n因為買到HKEXPRESS平機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22acb919e7fc08a543e4c716486a54281274009","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"因為無意中見到芽莊好似幾靚<br />\n就上網睇機票 見UO有平機票 連稅6百有找<br />\n但唔係日日有航班 仲要來回都得早機<br />\n最後去左四日 網上申請approval letter<br />\n去到當地先再搞落地簽"},{"pid":"7e7c938c03a768071cadb1fe5f525986af4c25e7","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"Day 1 <br />\n<br />\nCHO DAM MARKET<br />\n芽莊教堂<br />\n<br />\nDAY 2<br />\n<br />\n芽莊沙灘<br />\n泥漿浴 <br />\n占婆塔<br />\n<br />\nDAY 3<br />\n<br />\n潛水<br />\n市集大街"},{"pid":"8fd9e17c40d88be63614cdd574bc55745463fc6e","tid":397650,"uid":125090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:22:44.000Z","msg":"留名睇吓係咪咁靚"},{"pid":"05e9ce8251e244fa440e6e420fc86fee2b3d695d","tid":397650,"uid":137462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"Stay過芽莊一日<br />\n淨係去左占婆廟同I Resort<br />\n其他等樓主介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9de9360f973d179817180fdf18163e2d74c33c2","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Stay過芽莊一日<br />\n淨係去左占婆廟同I Resort<br />\n其他等樓主介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身想join四島游 姐係一班人包船去四個島 可以去水族館 跳水 滑翔傘 但我唔係樣樣有興趣 所以無join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0473a67af94b13c66bf21ef5b1bcf883642354","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"Day1<br />\n<br />\n去左市集同芽莊教堂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我搞落地簽 去之前上網申請 比6美金<br />\nouterbay返落車就見到整落地簽counter<br />\n排隊交低passport approval letter等叫名<br />\n<br />\n架機8成人都係落地簽 等左一個鐘<br />\n聽到名比25美金就可以拎返passport<br />\n簽證就貼左係passport入面<br />\n<br />\n行出機場過馬路就有巴士買飛counter<br />\n一張50k越南盾(VND)上車有人問你去邊<br />\n你講低到站佢就會叫你落車<br />\n<br />\n酒店我就住沙灘對面 個到一條街都係三星酒店<br />\n一落車過馬路就到左酒店 放低個袋就出發<br />\n<br />\nReception態度幾好 識英文<br />\n咁我就問佢Cho Dam Market有咩車去<br />\n佢就話對面有巴士 搭04號巴士<br />\n架巴士好平 7k VND 搭10分鐘左右就到<br />\n<br />\n但去到發現佢地收檔 得幾間未收<br />\n都係賣手信 榴槤餅 茶葉個d<br />\n之後坐當地人既電單車去芽莊教堂<br />\n周街都係當地人揸電單車 做乘客係幾爽既 不過佢地個頭盔好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n教堂入場唔洗錢 但唔可以背心短褲入<br />\n用外套笠一笠都入得<br />\n唔洗入場費可以去睇下 幾靚～"},{"pid":"690c8121ea03a457b9859a342de69121ccafc9fe","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/003113_fef4b220bfa0fc539c4e503a1b4e9875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F003113_fef4b220bfa0fc539c4e503a1b4e9875.jpg&h=bbac9edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店間房有浴缸 都叫望到海<br />\n但床單唔乾淨 好似訓完周身痕咁"},{"pid":"747dcdbe78232c65ede58f7c632529d259a632df","tid":397650,"uid":18266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b15f933b1ce8e44e8bc08f15df9a58f23b60180c","tid":397650,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"治安點？<br />\n有無多啲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5944bf925fcd8d88dcc78e738796906e33bce8","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:51:37.000Z","msg":"Day2 <br />\n<br />\n8am左右起身 係酒店食左早餐<br />\n<br />\n求其食左d就出發去酒店附近間Sailing Club報名潛水  但報完day3先有得潛<br />\n<br />\n之後出發去必去既泥漿浴同占婆塔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/004734_9195109c1bf7575692b32ddc6a2d25c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F004734_9195109c1bf7575692b32ddc6a2d25c0.jpg&h=57d36b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢到係岩岩比完錢 入左場後 <br />\n<br />\n酒店可以幫你book車去 60k VND包來回<br />\n會接埋附近酒店其他人 平過自己截的士<br />\n我就浸公共池 180k VND 入到比20k locker鎖匙按金就可以換泳衣浸<br />\n<br />\n個池可以坐6-8人 浸廿分鐘有人會叫你起身<br />\n浸落去個感覺幾舒服 有d磨砂粒咁<br />\n浸完認為個人浴/家庭浴會舒服d 但貴好多 我貪平所以揀公共池<br />\n手機唔防水所以無帶入池影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f66a4a0d6f15752e7fe9de9e43aedf6550a890","tid":397650,"uid":16176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得治安無大家想像中咁差<br />\n可能呢區太多遊客 鬼佬佔最多<br />\n但周街都係電單車同的士佬兜客"}]}